  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "rylor_backpack_quest",
      "name": "Rylor_Backpack Quest",
      "description": "",
      "startNodeId": "rylor_backpack_quest_start",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "rylor_backpack_quest_start",
          "text": "You found it! And quick timing, too. Another hour longer of searching and I'm not sure we'd make it back in one piece! Let's start heading back to town.\n\nClick the square to the right of our current area on the minimap to travel to it. ",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "rylor_backpack_quest_start_option_1",
              "text": "Lets head out!",
              "closeDialogue": true
            }
          ],
          "onEnterEffects": [
            {
              "type": "complete_quest",
              "questId": "find_your_backpack"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "folder": "Rylor"
    },
    {
      "id": "rylor_clear_the_danger_complete",
      "name": "Rylor - Clear the Danger Complete",
      "description": "Rylor returns to dialogue after helping the player clear the farmstead threat.",
      "startNodeId": "rylor_clear_the_danger_complete_start",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "rylor_clear_the_danger_complete_start",
          "text": "That should hold the Threadhorns back for now. The Farmstead can breathe again, at least for a little while.",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "rylor_clear_the_danger_complete_start_option_1",
              "text": "Glad you're safe.",
              "closeDialogue": true,
              "effects": [
                {
                  "type": "complete_quest",
                  "questId": "clear_the_danger"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "folder": "Rylor"
    },
    {
      "id": "rylor_farmstead_1",
      "name": "Rylor_Farmstead_1",
      "description": "",
      "startNodeId": "rylor_farmstead_1_start",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "rylor_farmstead_1_start",
          "text": "[narration] Rylor smells the air. His Bioboard whirrs with anticipatory energy [/narration] The air stirs with unrest. I fear we are in the company of hostile fauna. [narration] Rylor readies his sword [narration].",
          "options": [],
          "continueLabel": "Continue",
          "nextNodeId": "rylor_farmstead_1_node_2"
        },
        {
          "id": "rylor_farmstead_1_node_2",
          "text": "[narration] He smiles at you and one of his eyebrows juts[/narration].  You know how to use your sword, right? Just start swinging!",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "rylor_farmstead_1_node_2_option_1",
              "text": "For Lyoris!",
              "closeDialogue": true,
              "effects": [
                {
                  "type": "spawn_interactable",
                  "interactableId": "threadhorn_staglet"
                },
                {
                  "type": "grant_quest",
                  "questId": "clear_the_danger"
                },
                {
                  "type": "transform_interactable",
                  "target": "bearer",
                  "interactableId": "rylor_combat"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "folder": "Rylor"
    },
    {
      "id": "rylor_instructions",
      "name": "rylor_instructions",
      "description": "While the player is on the quest 'Find Your Backpack', if you talk to Rylor during this quest, he will point you towards exploring.",
      "startNodeId": "rylor_instructions_start",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "rylor_instructions_start",
          "text": "Hit the \"Explore\" button on the top right of your screen to explore this area. Perhaps you left your backpack somewhere while gathering berries?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "rylor_instructions_start_option_1",
              "text": "Roger that.",
              "closeDialogue": true
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "folder": "Rylor"
    },
    {
      "id": "rylor_intro",
      "name": "Rylor Intro",
      "description": "",
      "startNodeId": "rylor_intro_start",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "id": "rylor_intro_start",
          "text": "Who knew cutting dead plants could work up such an appetite? [narration] He lets out an exacerbated sigh as he picks up his backpack [/narration].",
          "options": [],
          "nextNodeId": "rylor_intro_node_2",
          "continueLabel": "Continue"
        },
        {
          "id": "rylor_intro_node_2",
          "text": "The sky is tired. We should head back before it gets too dangerous out here. [narration] He looks around, and then looks at you, confused. [/narration]. Where did you leave your backpack?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "rylor_intro_node_2_option_1",
              "text": "I'm not too sure.",
              "nextNodeId": "rylor_intro_node_3"
            }
          ],
          "continueLabel": "Continue",
          "onEnterEffects": [],
          "nextNodeId": "rylor_intro_node_3"
        },
        {
          "id": "rylor_intro_node_3",
          "text": "Ha! And I thought I was delirious. Well, we don't want you returning to Virelios without any haul, so let's try to find it.\n\nHit the [color=#FFA74E] Explore [/color] button on the top right of your screen to navigate around this area. I'm sure it will come up sooner rather than later.",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "rylor_intro_node_3_option_1",
              "text": "Will do!",
              "closeDialogue": true,
              "effects": [
                {
                  "type": "grant_quest",
                  "questId": "find_your_backpack"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "onEnterEffects": []
        }
      ],
      "folder": "Rylor"
    }
  ],
